# ==========================================
#     Local Config & Credentials Fallbacks
# ==========================================
# Prevent developer secrets from leaking into Git.
# If developers choose to hardcode their keys inside config.yaml, 
# it's best to keep a clean config.yaml.example tracked in git,
# and ignore the active config.yaml.
# For simplicity, we track a default template, but developers
# should use environment variables instead of hardcoding.
# config.yaml

